    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/fe6c6bbf18c58ed73565648232b994b9.poster.avif?t=1768520174\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/fe6c6bbf18c58ed73565648232b994b9.webm?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/fe6c6bbf18c58ed73565648232b994b9.mp4?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一层都是全新的体验。<strong>解开复杂的谜题</strong>，<strong>完成任务</strong>，<strong>寻找工具</strong>。要小心--每个角落都有陷阱、可怕的生物和惊喜。保持头脑清醒，与朋友合作，向未知领域挺进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/5224d76190c0998bb97a94cee2714d5e.poster.avif?t=1768520174\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/5224d76190c0998bb97a94cee2714d5e.webm?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/5224d76190c0998bb97a94cee2714d5e.mp4?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/67eea60651cefdb1a16c01d4063614c9.poster.avif?t=1768520174\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/67eea60651cefdb1a16c01d4063614c9.webm?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/67eea60651cefdb1a16c01d4063614c9.mp4?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们有些连最轻微的声音都能听到，所以一定要小心。注意你发出的声音，当它们靠近时不要太大声说话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/dd332b17b8c4926c0dfbc5b7c3bcd922.poster.avif?t=1768520174\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/dd332b17b8c4926c0dfbc5b7c3bcd922.webm?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/dd332b17b8c4926c0dfbc5b7c3bcd922.mp4?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/8efa86e734fe21012f7a743f94c8a48d.poster.avif?t=1768520174\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/8efa86e734fe21012f7a743f94c8a48d.webm?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147200/extras/8efa86e734fe21012f7a743f94c8a48d.mp4?t=1768520174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找人帮忙，最好不要一个人去。危险总是存在的，最好是一起应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
